      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Basic Prefix Sum Array (n + 1 version)\n\nint[] arr = {2, 4, 1, 7, 3};\nint n = arr.length;\n\nlong[] pref = new long[n + 1];\n\nfor (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    pref[i + 1] = pref[i] + arr[i];\n}\n\nlong sum = pref[r + 1] - pref[l];",
      "fontSize": 25.42857142857145,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Basic Prefix Sum Array (n + 1 version)\n\nint[] arr = {2, 4, 1, 7, 3};\nint n = arr.length;\n\nlong[] pref = new long[n + 1];\n\nfor (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    pref[i + 1] = pref[i] + arr[i];\n}\n\nlong sum = pref[r + 1] - pref[l];",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
